Major changes in this repository:
- Added a simplified Gradio demo for MiniCPM-V 4.6 local multimodal inference.
- Added local setup and usage documentation.
- Added a PyAV-based video decoding workaround for macOS environments where torchvision video decoding is unavailable.
- Added localhost/no_proxy handling for more reliable local Gradio startup.
- Removed unused legacy demos, evaluation code, old assets, and unrelated documentation from the original repository.

Model weights are not redistributed in this repository. Users should download or cache the model from the official Hugging Face repository:
https://huggingface.co/openbmb/MiniCPM-V-4.6
